23 than August 1, 2026.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Board of Regents shall provide staff support
25 for the task force, and the legislative auditor shall provide actuarial services upon request.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that members shall serve without compensation.
27 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the task force shall submit a written report of
